  },
  {
   "start": 123.6,
   "end": 126.08,
   "text": "We're going to need to either build one or rent one.",
   "speaker": "S22"
  },
  {
   "start": 126.22,
   "end": 129.78,
   "text": "And Brendon, I'm thinking we're going to need a flock of pigeons and a bird wrangler.",
   "speaker": "S05"
  },
  {
   "start": 129.9,
   "end": 132.58,
   "text": "Right, and I have 14 minutes of uninterrupted CG.",
