  },
  {
   "start": 133.64,
   "end": 135.26,
   "text": "Oh, it's computer graphics.",
   "speaker": "S22"
  },
  {
   "start": 135.92,
   "end": 138.32,
   "text": "So we'll need that for the cow's dream sequence.",
   "speaker": "S22"
  },
  {
   "start": 138.5,
   "end": 138.8,
   "text": "Definitely.",
   "speaker": "S22"
  },
  {
   "start": 139.22,
   "end": 143.2,
   "text": "We need an ice sculptor and an ice puppeteer, which I'm not sure if it exists, but we need to find one.",
   "speaker": "S05"
  },
  {
   "start": 143.4,
   "end": 143.8,
   "text": "Socks.",
   "speaker": "S05"
  },
  {
   "start": 143.92,
   "end": 144.6,
   "text": "Grandfather clock.",
   "speaker": "S05"
  },
  {
   "start": 145.0,
   "end": 145.4,
   "text": "Kilts.",
   "speaker": "S05"
  },
  {
   "start": 145.56,
   "end": 145.96,
   "text": "Scooby gear.",
   "speaker": "S05"
  },
  {
   "start": 146.08,
   "end": 146.4,
   "text": "Right.",
   "speaker": "S05"
  },
  {
   "start": 146.52,
   "end": 147.3,
   "text": "A horse and buggy.",
   "speaker": "S22"
  },
  {
   "start": 147.4,
   "end": 147.9,
   "text": "A robot.",
   "speaker": "S22"
  },
  {
   "start": 148.22,
   "end": 150.22,
   "text": "And finally, plutonium.",
