   "end": 199.96,
   "text": "Brandon!",
   "speaker": "S06"
  },
  {
   "start": 201.16,
   "end": 202.78,
   "text": "Where's my childhood gone, Josie?",
   "speaker": "S06"
  },
  {
   "start": 203.2,
   "end": 205.82,
   "text": "Maybe we'll just have been looking at the books, which we don't have.",
   "speaker": "S22"
  },
  {
   "start": 205.96,
   "end": 208.32,
   "text": "But if we had books, they'd say that we're out of money, right?",
   "speaker": "S22"
  },
  {
   "start": 208.48,
   "end": 209.44,
   "text": "Yeah, but we're close.",
   "speaker": "S05"
  },
  {
   "start": 209.62,
   "end": 210.26,
   "text": "Money's what we need.",
   "speaker": "S22"
  },
  {
   "start": 210.4,
   "end": 214.48,
   "text": "But guys, maybe this isn't the movie we sink all our time and energy into.",
