  {
   "start": 255.14,
   "end": 256.02,
   "text": "It's our best musical.",
   "speaker": "S05"
  },
  {
   "start": 256.84,
   "end": 264.5,
   "text": "There's a unique experience that you can feel when you watch a film that has this type of movie.",
   "speaker": "S05"
  },
  {
   "start": 264.8,
   "end": 266.28,
   "text": "It's an experience that you'll never forget.",
   "speaker": "S22"
  },
  {
   "start": 266.28,
   "end": 267.68,
   "text": "It's a fairy tale, I would say.",
   "speaker": "S05"
  },
  {
   "start": 268.64,
   "end": 270.28,
   "text": "Okay, so that didn't go so well.",
   "speaker": "S05"
  },
  {
   "start": 270.58,
   "end": 271.8,
   "text": "Well, it looks like it's kind of over.",
   "speaker": "S06"
  },
  {
   "start": 272.58,
   "end": 274.32,
   "text": "Well, no, I mean, we can think of other people.",
   "speaker": "S05"
  },
  {
   "start": 274.56,
   "end": 275.48,
   "text": "What about Coach McGurk?",
   "speaker": "S05"
  },
  {
   "start": 275.6,
   "end": 276.4,
   "text": "I don't know.",
   "speaker": "S06"
  },
  {
   "start": 276.4,
   "end": 278.38,
   "text": "Oh, yeah, Brendon, Coach McGurk will give you money.",
   "speaker": "S22"
  },
  {
   "start": 278.6,
   "end": 279.9,
   "text": "He doesn't want to invest.",
   "speaker": "S06"
  },
  {
   "start": 280.16,
   "end": 280.72,
   "text": "How do you know?",
   "speaker": "S06"
  },
  {
   "start": 281.04,
   "end": 282.3,
   "text": "He'll spend his money on anything.",
   "speaker": "S05"
  },
  {
   "start": 283.94,
   "end": 285.74,
   "text": "Welcome back to the Shop at Your House Network.",
   "speaker": "S04"
  },
  {
   "start": 286.02,
   "end": 287.04,
   "text": "Next up is Mappy.",
   "speaker": "S04"
  },
  {
   "start": 287.28,
   "end": 288.72,
   "text": "I love Mappy.",
   "speaker": "S151"
  },
  {
   "start": 289.12,
   "end": 290.94,
   "text": "Oh, and he's got a real excited look on his face.",
   "speaker": "S04"
  },
  {
   "start": 291.06,
   "end": 292.38,
   "text": "Why are you so excited, Mappy?",
   "speaker": "S175"
  },
  {
   "start": 292.48,
   "end": 293.14,
   "text": "Come over here.",
   "speaker": "S175"
  },
  {
   "start": 293.22,
   "end": 294.02,
   "text": "Tell us why, Mappy.",
   "speaker": "S22"
  },
  {
   "start": 294.14,
   "end": 294.56,
   "text": "Swords!",
   "speaker": "S22"
  },
  {
   "start": 295.54,
   "end": 295.98,
   "text": "Swords!",
   "speaker": "S22"
  },
  {
   "start": 296.08,
   "end": 297.34,
   "text": "Oh, look at those.",
   "speaker": "S172"
  },
  {
   "start": 297.54,
   "end": 299.26,
   "text": "I'm selling the ultimate sword package.",
   "speaker": "S172"
  },
  {
   "start": 299.48,
   "end": 300.5,
   "text": "What's included in that?",
   "speaker": "S173"
  },
  {
   "start": 300.56,
   "end": 301.76,
   "text": "Well, hopefully some bandages.",
   "speaker": "S04"
  },
  {
   "start": 302.72,
   "end": 305.82,
   "text": "All kinds of swords finely crafted, finely crafted.",
   "speaker": "S172"
  },
  {
   "start": 305.86,
   "end": 306.58,
   "text": "They're beautiful.",
   "speaker": "S175"
  },
  {
   "start": 306.8,
   "end": 307.32,
   "text": "They really are.",
   "speaker": "S175"
  },
  {
   "start": 307.54,
   "end": 308.8,
   "text": "You can see a reflection in them.",
   "speaker": "S05"
  },
  {
   "start": 308.9,
   "end": 313.6,
   "text": "I can see these behind glass in a living room or a den in middle America.",
   "speaker": "S04"
  },
  {
   "start": 313.8,
   "end": 315.12,
   "text": "You paint a pretty picture.",
   "speaker": "S175"
  },
  {
   "start": 315.12,
   "end": 317.74,
   "text": "Put over a hearth or a furnace or whatever you have.",
   "speaker": "S04"
  },
  {
   "start": 317.9,
   "end": 319.86,
   "text": "I would see these over my work area.",
   "speaker": "S04"
  },
  {
   "start": 319.88,
   "end": 320.7,
   "text": "As a wall hanging.",
   "speaker": "S05"
  },
  {
   "start": 320.8,
   "end": 325.18,
   "text": "Down in the basement where I can come down alone after an argument with my wife.",
   "speaker": "S04"
  },
  {
   "start": 325.44,
   "end": 325.7,
   "text": "Exactly.",
   "speaker": "S04"
  },
  {
   "start": 325.9,
   "end": 326.68,
   "text": "And look at the swords.",
   "speaker": "S04"
  },
  {
   "start": 327.06,
   "end": 328.04,
   "text": "Take them out too.",
   "speaker": "S172"
  },
  {
   "start": 328.26,
   "end": 328.92,
   "text": "And sharpen them.",
   "speaker": "S04"
  },
  {
   "start": 329.08,
   "end": 330.44,
   "text": "Swing them around in your backyard.",
   "speaker": "S172"
  },
  {
   "start": 330.6,
   "end": 331.68,
   "text": "Yeah, and just have fun with them.",
   "speaker": "S04"
  },
  {
   "start": 331.76,
   "end": 332.52,
   "text": "Listen to this sound.",
   "speaker": "S06"
  },
  {
   "start": 332.86,
   "end": 332.96,
   "text": "Yeah.",
   "speaker": "S06"
  },
  {
   "start": 333.54,
   "end": 333.9,
   "text": "Wow.",
   "speaker": "S06"
  },
  {
   "start": 334.32,
   "end": 335.06,
   "text": "It's beautiful.",
   "speaker": "S90"
  },
  {
   "start": 335.28,
   "end": 335.6,
   "text": "Listen again.",
   "speaker": "S90"
  },
  {
   "start": 335.78,
   "end": 336.24,
   "text": "That is, yeah.",
   "speaker": "S90"
  },
  {
   "start": 336.78,
   "end": 339.46,
   "text": "God, you could almost record that and make a musical out of it.",
   "speaker": "S04"
  },
  {
   "start": 339.58,
   "end": 340.3,
   "text": "I would buy it.",
   "speaker": "S151"
  },
  {
   "start": 340.3,
   "end": 340.7,
   "text": "Yeah, yeah.",
   "speaker": "S151"
  },
  {
   "start": 340.7,
   "end": 342.0,
   "text": "I would buy a CD of that sound.",
   "speaker": "S175"
  },
  {
   "start": 342.0,
   "end": 343.84,
   "text": "Now we have only 13 minutes left on this.",
   "speaker": "S04"
  },
  {
   "start": 343.98,
   "end": 344.5,
   "text": "Hurry up the sun.",
   "speaker": "S04"
  },
  {
   "start": 344.5,
   "end": 345.08,
   "text": "Special deal.",
   "speaker": "S04"
  },
  {
   "start": 345.2,
   "end": 345.56,
   "text": "Swords.",
   "speaker": "S04"
  },
  {
   "start": 346.08,
   "end": 347.12,
   "text": "I mean, take another...",
   "speaker": "S04"
  },
  {
   "start": 347.12,
   "end": 348.74,
   "text": "Let's get another close-up of this.",
   "speaker": "S04"
  },
  {
   "start": 348.98,
   "end": 349.34,
   "text": "Swords.",
   "speaker": "S04"
  },
  {
   "start": 355.06,
   "end": 355.92,
   "text": "Those are awesome.",
   "speaker": "S06"
  },
  {
   "start": 356.1,
   "end": 357.1,
   "text": "No, they're not awesome.",
   "speaker": "S04"
  },
  {
   "start": 357.32,
   "end": 360.22,
   "text": "There's a big difference between awesome and extremely expensive.",
   "speaker": "S04"
  },
  {
   "start": 360.54,
   "end": 362.38,
   "text": "So how did you get the money to buy all those swords?",
   "speaker": "S06"
  },
  {
   "start": 362.46,
   "end": 363.1,
   "text": "That's just so cool.",
   "speaker": "S06"
  },
  {
   "start": 363.3,
   "end": 365.52,
   "text": "I don't have the money to buy all these swords.",
   "speaker": "S04"
  },
  {
   "start": 365.76,
   "end": 366.46,
   "text": "Well, how do you get them?",
   "speaker": "S06"
  },
  {
   "start": 366.54,
   "end": 367.44,
   "text": "I gotta return them.",
   "speaker": "S04"
  },
  {
   "start": 367.68,
   "end": 368.04,
   "text": "Why?",
   "speaker": "S04"
  },
  {
   "start": 368.32,
   "end": 369.82,
   "text": "Because I don't want swords, Brendon.",
   "speaker": "S04"
  },
  {
   "start": 369.82,
   "end": 370.56,
   "text": "Why don't you want swords?",
   "speaker": "S172"
  },
  {
   "start": 370.64,
   "end": 371.7,
   "text": "Who would want swords?",
   "speaker": "S04"
  },
  {
   "start": 371.88,
   "end": 372.28,
   "text": "I do.",
   "speaker": "S04"
  },
  {
   "start": 372.58,
   "end": 373.58,
   "text": "All right, you wanna buy them?",
   "speaker": "S04"
  },
  {
   "start": 373.74,
   "end": 374.08,
   "text": "No.",
   "speaker": "S04"
  },
  {
   "start": 374.08,
   "end": 374.58,
   "text": "Why?",
   "speaker": "S04"
  },
  {
   "start": 374.86,
   "end": 375.66,
   "text": "Because I don't have any money.",
   "speaker": "S06"
  },
  {
   "start": 375.86,
   "end": 379.16,
   "text": "Well, then you're sharing and understanding my problem.",
   "speaker": "S04"
  },
  {
   "start": 379.36,
   "end": 380.0,
   "text": "Why'd you buy them?",
   "speaker": "S06"
  },
  {
   "start": 380.18,
   "end": 381.4,
   "text": "Well, it's complicated, Brendon.",
   "speaker": "S04"
  },
  {
   "start": 381.52,
   "end": 382.08,
   "text": "Well, what's the complicated?",
   "speaker": "S04"
  },
  {
   "start": 382.12,
   "end": 382.86,
   "text": "I can understand it.",
   "speaker": "S06"
  },
  {
   "start": 382.88,
   "end": 383.0,
   "text": "Why?",
   "speaker": "S06"
  },
  {
   "start": 383.2,
   "end": 383.94,
   "text": "You don't understand.",
   "speaker": "S04"
  },
  {
   "start": 384.0,
   "end": 384.96,
   "text": "No, I could probably understand.",
   "speaker": "S06"
  },
  {
   "start": 385.16,
   "end": 387.16,
   "text": "You would never understand unless you lived alone.",
   "speaker": "S04"
  },
  {
   "start": 387.52,
   "end": 389.88,
   "text": "So you live by yourself and want you get lonely and buy swords?",
   "speaker": "S06"
  },
  {
   "start": 390.02,
   "end": 390.54,
   "text": "I don't understand.",
   "speaker": "S06"
  },
  {
   "start": 391.22,
   "end": 392.0,
   "text": "Well, you nailed it.",
   "speaker": "S04"
  },
  {
   "start": 392.52,
   "end": 392.96,
   "text": "That's it?",
   "speaker": "S04"
  },
  {
   "start": 393.14,
   "end": 393.54,
   "text": "Yeah.",
   "speaker": "S04"
  },
  {
   "start": 394.06,
   "end": 396.66,
   "text": "So you probably won't be investing in my movie then.",
   "speaker": "S06"
  },
  {
   "start": 396.92,
   "end": 398.84,
   "text": "No, if it requires money.",
   "speaker": "S04"
  },
  {
   "start": 399.04,
   "end": 399.3,
   "text": "Yes.",
   "speaker": "S04"
  },
  {
   "start": 399.68,
   "end": 401.38,
   "text": "Now, who cares about this stupid movie?",
   "speaker": "S06"
  },
  {
   "start": 401.48,
   "end": 403.66,
   "text": "It's the biggest piece of crap I've ever been involved in.",
   "speaker": "S06"
  },
  {
   "start": 404.08,
   "end": 407.44,
   "text": "I would rather do anything than work right now.",
   "speaker": "S06"
  },
  {
   "start": 407.68,
   "end": 409.8,
   "text": "I mean, I should be doing stupid kid stuff, you know?",
   "speaker": "S06"
  },
  {
   "start": 410.36,
   "end": 412.84,
   "text": "Look around this field. Look at these kids. They're just having fun.",
   "speaker": "S06"
  },
  {
   "start": 412.98,
   "end": 413.86,
   "text": "Look at Jeremy over there.",
   "speaker": "S06"
  },
  {
   "start": 414.12,
   "end": 416.94,
   "text": "He doesn't have a care in the world. He just goes home and eats cookies.",
   "speaker": "S06"
  },
  {
   "start": 417.04,
   "end": 419.12,
   "text": "I talk to him all the time. I say, what did you do last night?",
   "speaker": "S06"
  },
  {
   "start": 419.12,
   "end": 421.52,
   "text": "He goes, I went home and ate cookies, and I had peanut butter and jelly sandwich.",
   "speaker": "S06"
  },
  {
   "start": 421.98,
   "end": 422.42,
   "text": "That's it.",
   "speaker": "S06"
  },
  {
   "start": 422.66,
   "end": 423.38,
   "text": "But he's obese.",
   "speaker": "S04"
  },
  {
   "start": 424.26,
   "end": 424.98,
   "text": "He's a big kid.",
   "speaker": "S06"
  },
  {
   "start": 425.58,
   "end": 427.08,
   "text": "You know, these are actually pretty cool.",
   "speaker": "S04"
  },
  {
   "start": 427.4,
   "end": 430.42,
   "text": "The only reason I have anything to do with this dumb piece of crap",
   "speaker": "S06"
  },
  {
   "start": 430.42,
   "end": 432.54,
   "text": "Is because Jason and Melissa are so excited about it.",
   "speaker": "S06"
  },
  {
   "start": 432.54,
   "end": 433.1,
   "text": "Brendon Duck.",
   "speaker": "S06"
  },
  {
   "start": 433.1,
   "end": 434.22,
   "text": "Whoa, okay, whoa.",
   "speaker": "S06"
  },
  {
   "start": 434.78,
   "end": 436.1,
   "text": "That's not, that was really close.",
   "speaker": "S06"
  },
  {
   "start": 436.14,
   "end": 436.68,
   "text": "Jump, Brendon.",
   "speaker": "S06"
  },
  {
   "start": 437.18,
   "end": 437.8,
   "text": "Oh my God.",
   "speaker": "S06"
  },
  {
   "start": 438.0,
   "end": 439.02,
   "text": "Hold up that soccer ball.",
   "speaker": "S04"
  },
  {
   "start": 439.2,
   "end": 439.34,
   "text": "No.",
   "speaker": "S04"
  },
  {
   "start": 439.52,
   "end": 439.84,
   "text": "Come on.",
   "speaker": "S04"
  },
  {
   "start": 440.0,
   "end": 440.12,
   "text": "No.",
   "speaker": "S04"
  },
  {
   "start": 440.28,
   "end": 441.04,
   "text": "Brendon, it'll be fun.",
   "speaker": "S04"
  },
  {
   "start": 441.18,
   "end": 441.36,
   "text": "No.",
   "speaker": "S04"
  },
  {
   "start": 441.44,
   "end": 442.14,
   "text": "I'll cut it in half.",
   "speaker": "S04"
  },
  {
   "start": 442.32,
   "end": 443.16,
   "text": "Coach, you're gonna kill me.",
   "speaker": "S06"
  },
  {
   "start": 443.28,
   "end": 444.92,
   "text": "Hold it above your head so I don't hit your head.",
   "speaker": "S04"
  },
  {
   "start": 445.1,
   "end": 445.26,
   "text": "Okay.",
   "speaker": "S04"
  },
  {
   "start": 445.58,
   "end": 446.06,
   "text": "All right, ready?",
   "speaker": "S04"
  },
  {
   "start": 446.42,
   "end": 447.0,
   "text": "Don't kill me.",
   "speaker": "S04"
  },
  {
   "start": 447.06,
   "end": 447.94,
   "text": "Don't close your eyes.",
   "speaker": "S04"
  },
  {
   "start": 448.12,
   "end": 448.86,
   "text": "I want you to see it.",
   "speaker": "S04"
  },
  {
   "start": 448.94,
   "end": 449.38,
   "text": "Hey, Coach.",
   "speaker": "S04"
  },
  {
   "start": 449.8,
   "end": 451.58,
   "text": "Me and Eugene gotta go early today.",
   "speaker": "S57"
  },
  {
   "start": 452.0,
   "end": 453.08,
   "text": "Here is a note.",
   "speaker": "S176"
  },
  {
   "start": 453.36,
   "end": 455.0,
   "text": "What, you guys got another skunk scout meeting?",
   "speaker": "S04"
  },
  {
   "start": 455.16,
   "end": 455.42,
   "text": "Yeah.",
   "speaker": "S04"
  },
  {
   "start": 455.72,
   "end": 456.44,
   "text": "What, are you going to war?",
   "speaker": "S04"
  },
  {
   "start": 456.68,
   "end": 458.28,
   "text": "Ha, ha, ha, ha, very funny.",
   "speaker": "S57"
  },
  {
   "start": 458.56,
   "end": 459.94,
   "text": "Hey, nice swords, Coach.",
   "speaker": "S57"
  },
  {
   "start": 460.2,
   "end": 460.34,
   "text": "Yeah.",
   "speaker": "S57"
  },
  {
   "start": 460.36,
   "end": 462.26,
   "text": "You are kung fu, uh, hot shot.",
   "speaker": "S176"
  },
  {
   "start": 463.06,
   "end": 464.32,
   "text": "Oh, hey, look, there's Brandon.",
   "speaker": "S57"
  },
  {
   "start": 464.44,
   "end": 465.28,
   "text": "We was gonna talk to him.",
   "speaker": "S57"
  },
  {
   "start": 465.68,
   "end": 468.2,
   "text": "Uh, Brandon, me and Eugene wanna talk to you about this.",
   "speaker": "S57"
  },
  {
   "start": 468.58,
   "end": 469.76,
   "text": "Maybe join the Skunk Scout.",
   "speaker": "S57"
  },
  {
   "start": 470.12,
   "end": 470.8,
   "text": "Really? Me?",
   "speaker": "S06"
  },
  {
   "start": 471.08,
   "end": 471.24,
   "text": "Yeah.",
   "speaker": "S06"
  },
  {
   "start": 471.34,
   "end": 472.26,
   "text": "Yeah, that's right, Brandon.",
   "speaker": "S57"
  },
  {
   "start": 472.26,
   "end": 473.86,
   "text": "We think we'll make a pretty good Skunk Scout.",
   "speaker": "S57"
  },
  {
   "start": 474.02,
   "end": 476.74,
   "text": "And also, me and Eugene get a badge for that.",
   "speaker": "S57"
  },
  {
   "start": 476.88,
   "end": 480.1,
   "text": "Yeah, I can't really go and join the Skunk Scouts right now.",
   "speaker": "S06"
  },
  {
   "start": 480.14,
   "end": 482.24,
   "text": "I gotta find investors for this movie.",
   "speaker": "S06"
  },
  {
   "start": 482.56,
   "end": 484.6,
   "text": "You, uh, learn to defend yourself in fire?",
   "speaker": "S176"
  },
  {
   "start": 485.08,
   "end": 487.58,
   "text": "We learn how to sew, like, if your short gets a rip.",
   "speaker": "S57"
  },
  {
   "start": 487.58,
   "end": 493.02,
   "text": "We learn how to make a stick and you know hunt fish and kill bear one time",
   "speaker": "S176"
  },
  {
   "start": 493.02,
   "end": 494.94,
   "text": "We come so close to killing a bear",
   "speaker": "S57"
  },
  {
   "start": 494.94,
   "end": 497.14,
   "text": "But the guy from the zoo was like get out of here",
   "speaker": "S57"
  },
  {
   "start": 497.14,
   "end": 501.88,
   "text": "And we almost kill a mountain lion and an alligator. We threw a penny on his head. I don't know guys",
   "speaker": "S57"
  },
  {
   "start": 501.88,
   "end": 507.68,
   "text": "I've got work to do you know we learn how to make socks out of short sleeves and how to make a Caesar salad",
   "speaker": "S57"
  },
  {
   "start": 509.06,
   "end": 515.72,
   "text": "And how to swim okay guys I should I you know that sounds that sounds like fun actually, but I gotta do this stupid movie",
   "speaker": "S06"
  },
  {
   "start": 515.72,
   "end": 516.66,
   "text": "I mean, when's the meeting?",
   "speaker": "S06"
  },
  {
   "start": 519.24,
   "end": 520.1,
   "text": "I'm sorry, Brendon.",
   "speaker": "S05"
  },
  {
   "start": 520.2,
   "end": 521.62,
   "text": "Why are you joining the Skunk Scouts?",
   "speaker": "S05"
  },
  {
   "start": 521.88,
   "end": 523.38,
   "text": "Yeah, Brendon, this is kind of bad timing.",
   "speaker": "S22"
  },
  {
   "start": 523.52,
   "end": 524.94,
   "text": "We sort of have a movie to sell.",
   "speaker": "S22"
  },
  {
   "start": 525.06,
   "end": 527.06,
   "text": "Guys, please, this is the most stressful day of my life.",
   "speaker": "S06"
  },
  {
   "start": 527.1,
   "end": 529.36,
   "text": "I'm being inducted into the Skunk Scouts.",
   "speaker": "S06"
  },
  {
   "start": 529.44,
   "end": 530.38,
   "text": "I don't need this drama.",
   "speaker": "S06"
  },
  {
   "start": 530.56,
   "end": 532.3,
   "text": "But what about getting investors for our movie?",
   "speaker": "S05"
  },
  {
   "start": 532.74,
   "end": 533.8,
   "text": "I'm working on it.",
   "speaker": "S06"
  },
  {
   "start": 534.36,
   "end": 537.08,
   "text": "With the Skunk Scout kids.",
   "speaker": "S06"
  },
  {
   "start": 537.76,
   "end": 538.12,
   "text": "Parents.",
   "speaker": "S06"
  },
  {
   "start": 539.0,
   "end": 540.6,
   "text": "They'll give us money.",
   "speaker": "S06"
  },
  {
   "start": 540.82,
   "end": 542.14,
   "text": "But we might need your help, Brendon.",
   "speaker": "S05"
  },
  {
   "start": 542.32,
   "end": 542.64,
   "text": "And you what?",
   "speaker": "S05"
  },
  {
   "start": 542.72,
   "end": 544.92,
   "text": "You guys are going door to door for the movie, right?",
   "speaker": "S06"
  },
  {
   "start": 544.92,
   "end": 547.74,
   "text": "I know, but the investors might want to meet the director, the writer.",
   "speaker": "S05"
  },
  {
   "start": 547.98,
   "end": 548.82,
   "text": "Okay, well, listen, listen.",
   "speaker": "S06"
  },
  {
   "start": 548.96,
   "end": 551.72,
   "text": "Call me when you need me to come in and close the deal, okay?",
   "speaker": "S06"
  },
  {
   "start": 551.98,
   "end": 554.54,
   "text": "All right, so Jason and I should start the pitch, and you'll be there to finish it.",
   "speaker": "S05"
  },
  {
   "start": 554.54,
   "end": 555.56,
   "text": "Yes, I'll get there.",
   "speaker": "S06"
  },
  {
   "start": 555.62,
   "end": 556.24,
   "text": "Don't worry.",
   "speaker": "S06"
  },
  {
   "start": 556.36,
   "end": 556.86,
   "text": "I get it.",
   "speaker": "S06"
  },
  {
   "start": 556.96,
   "end": 558.14,
   "text": "He shows up a little late.",
   "speaker": "S22"
  },
  {
   "start": 558.52,
   "end": 559.44,
   "text": "Like he's really busy.",
   "speaker": "S05"
  },
  {
   "start": 559.54,
   "end": 559.78,
   "text": "Right.",
   "speaker": "S05"
  },
  {
   "start": 560.02,
   "end": 560.64,
   "text": "I like it.",
   "speaker": "S05"
  },
  {
   "start": 560.72,
   "end": 561.36,
   "text": "I like it, too.",
   "speaker": "S22"
  },
  {
   "start": 561.56,
   "end": 562.24,
   "text": "Okay, great.",
   "speaker": "S06"
  },
  {
   "start": 562.7,
   "end": 565.0,
   "text": "Listen, Jason and I have some merchandise we'd like to show you.",
   "speaker": "S05"
  },
  {
   "start": 565.28,
   "end": 565.64,
   "text": "Fantastic.",
   "speaker": "S05"
  },
  {
   "start": 565.64,
   "end": 566.2,
   "text": "That's great.",
   "speaker": "S05"
  },
  {
   "start": 566.3,
   "end": 566.98,
   "text": "You guys are excited.",
   "speaker": "S06"
  },
  {
   "start": 567.08,
   "end": 567.44,
   "text": "You've been working.",
   "speaker": "S06"
  },
  {
   "start": 567.6,
   "end": 567.9,
   "text": "That's great.",
   "speaker": "S06"
  },
  {
   "start": 568.14,
   "end": 568.8,
   "text": "If you will.",
   "speaker": "S05"
  },
  {
   "start": 569.1,
   "end": 572.6,
   "text": "Okay, what we have here, Brendon, are the official Wizards Baker action figures.",
   "speaker": "S22"
  },
  {
   "start": 573.06,
   "end": 573.16,
   "text": "Ooh.",
   "speaker": "S22"
  },
  {
   "start": 573.78,
   "end": 574.14,
   "text": "Wow.",
   "speaker": "S22"
  },
  {
   "start": 574.14,
   "end": 575.86,
   "text": "Now here's your character, Brenda.",
   "speaker": "S22"
  },
  {
   "start": 576.48,
   "end": 578.26,
   "text": "Oh wait, hold on, that's Melissa's.",
   "speaker": "S22"
  },
  {
   "start": 578.32,
   "end": 578.88,
   "text": "That's Melissa's, okay.",
   "speaker": "S22"
  },
  {
   "start": 579.02,
   "end": 579.38,
   "text": "The goat.",
   "speaker": "S22"
  },
  {
   "start": 579.68,
   "end": 580.18,
   "text": "No, the cow.",
   "speaker": "S22"
  },
  {
   "start": 580.28,
   "end": 580.6,
   "text": "The cow.",
   "speaker": "S22"
  },
  {
   "start": 580.76,
   "end": 580.88,
   "text": "The cow.",
   "speaker": "S22"
  },
  {
   "start": 580.94,
   "end": 581.16,
   "text": "The cow.",
   "speaker": "S22"
  },
  {
   "start": 581.46,
   "end": 582.9,
   "text": "This is the cow, sort of.",
   "speaker": "S22"
  },
  {
   "start": 583.82,
   "end": 584.96,
   "text": "It's an action figure.",
   "speaker": "S22"
  },
  {
   "start": 585.24,
   "end": 585.44,
   "text": "Right.",
   "speaker": "S22"
  },
  {
   "start": 585.92,
   "end": 587.74,
   "text": "Are these the final versions?",
   "speaker": "S06"
  },
  {
   "start": 587.94,
   "end": 588.84,
   "text": "Yeah, of course they are.",
   "speaker": "S22"
  },
  {
   "start": 588.9,
   "end": 589.02,
   "text": "Why?",
   "speaker": "S22"
  },
  {
   "start": 589.72,
   "end": 591.84,
   "text": "Because I like them.",
   "speaker": "S06"
  },
  {
   "start": 592.04,
   "end": 593.16,
   "text": "Oh, and Melissa, the posters.",
   "speaker": "S22"
  },
  {
   "start": 593.34,
   "end": 593.94,
   "text": "Right, the posters.",
   "speaker": "S05"
  },
  {
   "start": 594.08,
   "end": 594.68,
   "text": "Posters, right.",
   "speaker": "S06"
  },
  {
   "start": 594.98,
   "end": 595.74,
   "text": "Melissa and I made posters.",
   "speaker": "S22"
  },
  {
   "start": 595.82,
   "end": 598.88,
   "text": "Yes, and these two are the final versions, approved by Jason and me.",
   "speaker": "S05"
  },
  {
   "start": 599.1,
   "end": 599.52,
   "text": "Oh, wow.",
   "speaker": "S05"
  },
  {
   "start": 599.62,
   "end": 600.3,
   "text": "Get a load of these.",
   "speaker": "S05"
  },
  {
   "start": 600.54,
   "end": 601.54,
   "text": "Whoa, hello.",
   "speaker": "S06"
  },
  {
   "start": 601.54,
   "end": 603.38,
   "text": "Oh, very good, very impressive.",
   "speaker": "S06"
  },
  {
   "start": 603.76,
   "end": 604.08,
   "text": "It's a beauty, right?",
   "speaker": "S06"
  },
  {
   "start": 604.32,
   "end": 606.32,
   "text": "Wait, guys, is this spelled right?",
   "speaker": "S06"
  },
  {
   "start": 606.52,
   "end": 608.0,
   "text": "W-I-Z-I-R-D?",
   "speaker": "S06"
  },
  {
   "start": 608.38,
   "end": 609.06,
   "text": "I'm not...",
   "speaker": "S151"
  },
  {
   "start": 609.06,
   "end": 609.28,
   "text": "Yeah.",
   "speaker": "S151"
  },
  {
   "start": 609.64,
   "end": 609.88,
   "text": "Jason?",
   "speaker": "S151"
  },
  {
   "start": 610.78,
   "end": 610.82,
   "text": "Uh...",
   "speaker": "S151"
  },
  {
   "start": 611.34,
   "end": 611.6,
   "text": "Yes.",
   "speaker": "S151"
  },
  {
   "start": 612.1,
   "end": 613.36,
   "text": "All right, well, good, great.",
   "speaker": "S06"
  },
  {
   "start": 613.6,
   "end": 614.24,
   "text": "See you later.",
   "speaker": "S90"
  },
  {
   "start": 614.92,
   "end": 620.2,
   "text": "As Den Leader Lennison of Troop Number Roman Numeral 43,",
   "speaker": "S58"
  },
  {
   "start": 620.24,
   "end": 625.7,
   "text": "I hereby say you are in...",
   "speaker": "S58"
  },
  {
   "start": 625.7,
   "end": 626.48,
   "text": "Hold it.",
   "speaker": "S58"
  },
  {
   "start": 626.78,
   "end": 628.74,
   "text": "The Skunk Scouts Now.",
   "speaker": "S58"
  },
  {
   "start": 629.04,
   "end": 629.56,
   "text": "Yes!",
   "speaker": "S58"
  },
  {
   "start": 630.76,
   "end": 631.32,
   "text": "Congratulations.",
   "speaker": "S58"
  },
  {
   "start": 631.9,
   "end": 633.38,
   "text": "Thank you. Thank you, everyone.",
   "speaker": "S06"
  },
  {
   "start": 634.2,
   "end": 635.6,
   "text": "Okay, I'll see you all of you next week.",
   "speaker": "S58"
  },
  {
   "start": 635.7,
   "end": 636.78,
   "text": "Thanks a lot. Have a nice evening.",
   "speaker": "S58"
  },
  {
   "start": 636.8,
   "end": 638.88,
   "text": "Mr. Lennison, hold on.",
   "speaker": "S57"
  },
  {
   "start": 639.18,
   "end": 641.92,
   "text": "We're supposed to talk about the Skunkwood Derby today.",
   "speaker": "S57"
  },
  {
   "start": 642.24,
   "end": 643.06,
   "text": "Can't follow you.",
   "speaker": "S58"
  },
  {
   "start": 643.24,
   "end": 644.0,
   "text": "I said, uh...",
   "speaker": "S57"
  },
  {
   "start": 644.0,
   "end": 646.48,
   "text": "The Derby with the vroom, vroom, vroom, vroom, vroom.",
   "speaker": "S176"
  },
  {
   "start": 646.68,
   "end": 648.22,
   "text": "Hold it, hard to concentrate.",
   "speaker": "S58"
  },
  {
   "start": 649.0,
   "end": 650.32,
   "text": "All right. Oh, here we go.",
   "speaker": "S58"
  },
  {
   "start": 650.46,
   "end": 654.94,
   "text": "You build a little car out of a little piece of 2x4",
   "speaker": "S58"
  },
  {
   "start": 654.94,
   "end": 656.96,
   "text": "And race it on a sloping track.",
   "speaker": "S58"
  },
  {
   "start": 657.34,
   "end": 658.44,
   "text": "Whatever that means.",
   "speaker": "S58"
  },
  {
   "start": 659.52,
   "end": 660.86,
   "text": "So do that.",
   "speaker": "S58"
  },
  {
   "start": 660.86,
   "end": 662.64,
   "text": "Is there any other questions?",
   "speaker": "S58"
  },
  {
   "start": 662.94,
   "end": 664.02,
   "text": "It's next week, right?",
   "speaker": "S57"
  },
  {
   "start": 664.22,
   "end": 665.42,
   "text": "I don't know.",
   "speaker": "S58"
  },
  {
   "start": 666.36,
   "end": 668.0,
   "text": "Next week, look at calendar.",
   "speaker": "S176"
  },
  {
   "start": 668.52,
   "end": 671.34,
   "text": "Afterward is spaghetti dinner, Mr. Linden-",
   "speaker": "S176"
  },
  {
   "start": 671.94,
   "end": 674.74,
   "text": "Okay, Mr. Attention to every detail.",
   "speaker": "S58"
  },
  {
   "start": 675.32,
   "end": 676.34,
   "text": "Hold on a second.",
   "speaker": "S58"
  },
  {
   "start": 676.6,
   "end": 678.2,
   "text": "Oh, okay, right, it's next week.",
   "speaker": "S58"
  },
  {
   "start": 680.32,
   "end": 681.46,
   "text": "Hello, sir and ma'am.",
   "speaker": "S22"
  },
  {
   "start": 681.58,
   "end": 684.08,
   "text": "Me and my friend Melissa, we'd only like a minute of your time.",
   "speaker": "S22"
  },
  {
   "start": 684.3,
   "end": 686.38,
   "text": "Yes, you. Do you like movies?",
   "speaker": "S05"
  },
  {
   "start": 686.68,
   "end": 687.22,
   "text": "Do you like money?",
   "speaker": "S05"
  },
  {
   "start": 687.48,
   "end": 689.78,
   "text": "Well, it's in your house. We're gonna make you rich.",
   "speaker": "S22"
  },
  {
   "start": 689.78,
   "end": 690.8,
   "text": "Rich, rich, rich.",
   "speaker": "S22"
  },
  {
   "start": 691.7,
   "end": 694.76,
   "text": "The projected movie's money back making are...",
   "speaker": "S05"
  },
  {
   "start": 694.76,
   "end": 694.78,
   "text": "Jason?",
   "speaker": "S05"
  },
  {
   "start": 695.3,
   "end": 696.3,
   "text": "Well, thank you, Melissa.",
   "speaker": "S22"
  },
  {
   "start": 696.3,
   "end": 698.62,
   "text": "We're looking at at least a few million.",
   "speaker": "S22"
  },
  {
   "start": 698.62,
   "end": 701.1,
   "text": "I would say in the ballpark of a million or more.",
   "speaker": "S22"
  },
  {
   "start": 701.26,
   "end": 702.3,
   "text": "I would say you're right, Jason.",
   "speaker": "S05"
  },
  {
   "start": 702.44,
   "end": 702.6,
   "text": "Yeah.",
   "speaker": "S05"
  },
  {
   "start": 702.8,
   "end": 706.04,
   "text": "And you'll be given a guarantee as a stock haver",
   "speaker": "S05"
  },
  {
   "start": 706.04,
   "end": 708.72,
   "text": "That the wizard's baker will indeed make...",
   "speaker": "S05"
  },
  {
   "start": 708.72,
   "end": 708.96,
   "text": "I'm sorry.",
   "speaker": "S05"
  },
  {
   "start": 709.14,
   "end": 710.1,
   "text": "One second, Melissa.",
   "speaker": "S22"
  },
  {
   "start": 710.24,
   "end": 711.98,
   "text": "What a beautiful baby.",
   "speaker": "S22"
  },
  {
   "start": 712.54,
   "end": 713.24,
   "text": "May I hold him?",
   "speaker": "S22"
  },
  {
   "start": 713.52,
   "end": 713.92,
   "text": "Is it a hammer?",
   "speaker": "S22"
  },
  {
   "start": 714.44,
   "end": 715.76,
   "text": "All right, listen carefully.",
   "speaker": "S04"
  },
  {
   "start": 715.88,
   "end": 717.64,
   "text": "I want to return the swords.",
   "speaker": "S04"
  },
  {
   "start": 718.06,
   "end": 718.76,
   "text": "That's all.",
   "speaker": "S04"
  },
  {
   "start": 718.76,
   "end": 720.82,
   "text": "That's all I want. I want my money back.",
   "speaker": "S04"
  },
  {
   "start": 720.84,
   "end": 722.22,
   "text": "And I already told you, sir.",
   "speaker": "S173"
  },
  {
   "start": 722.54,
   "end": 724.6,
   "text": "All cutlery is non-refundable.",
   "speaker": "S173"
  },
  {
   "start": 724.7,
   "end": 726.54,
   "text": "Ladies, swords are not cutlery.",
   "speaker": "S04"
  },
  {
   "start": 726.6,
   "end": 727.92,
   "text": "Well, we like to think they are.",
   "speaker": "S05"
  },
  {
   "start": 728.38,
   "end": 730.46,
   "text": "All right, that's it.",
   "speaker": "S04"
  },
  {
   "start": 730.56,
   "end": 732.98,
   "text": "I am going to use these swords in a...",
   "speaker": "S04"
  }
 ],
 "times": {
